# --- Submission cleanup -------------------------------------------------
# Only REPORT.pdf is the canonical submission artifact. The markdown source,
# DOCX exports, intermediate figures, and Claude-Code prompt scratchpad are
# kept locally for regeneration but excluded from the GitHub repo so judges
# see a minimal package: PDF report + code + data + README.

REPORT.md
REPORT.docx
REPORT_for_gdocs.md
REPORT_for_gdocs.docx
REPORT_figure1.png
CLAUDE_CODE_PROMPTS.md

# Local-only logs and scratch files
run.log
test.txt
*.log

# --- Python --------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
build/
dist/

# --- Virtual environments ------------------------------------------------
.venv/
venv/
env/

# --- IDE / OS ------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Tooling caches ------------------------------------------------------
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Cloned external dependencies ----------------------------------------
# ProteinMPNN is cloned during setup; users re-clone via the README.
# Comment this out if you want the cloned repo committed alongside.
external/

# --- HuggingFace model cache --------------------------------------------
# ESM-2 weights are downloaded automatically on first use. Don't commit
# them — they are large and reproducible.
.cache/
~/.cache/huggingface/

# --- Claude Code session metadata ---------------------------------------
.claude/

# --- Experimental data outputs (per "don't push any data") ---------------
# Code is published; raw per-sequence outputs and per-model calibration
# dumps are regenerable from a single demo run (see README + REPORT). The
# repo ships only the figures that the report embeds, not the underlying
# CSV / JSON / FASTA / PDB tables.
*.csv
*.npz
*.fasta
*.fa
results/scores.npz
results/summary.json
perplexity_guard/calibration/*.json
perplexity_guard/audit/results/*.json
perplexity_guard/demo_results/*.json
perplexity_guard/tests/sample_pdbs/*.pdb
